#quote(block: true, attribution: [Patrul Rinpoche @dalai-lama-dzogchen])[ // p.73
  In this way, always remind yourself of the view, which is the clear light
  recognized in you as your true nature, and rest in that state. Apart from that,
  the crucial point is neither to suppress nor indulge, neither accept nor reject,
  in any way, the thoughts or emotions which are the energy of rigpa:
  "Rest in the aspect of awareness, beyond all description."
